## FD10: Infra Dev-Tier (OpenTofu)
**Rules covered:** Sprint 2 §S2.1.1-§S2.1.4 acceptance criteria for `infra/dev-tier/*.tf`:
- `cloud-run.tf` — `min_instance_count = 0`, 1 vCPU / 2 GB, `timeout = 3600s`, `startup_cpu_boost = true`, dedicated `agent-middleware-runtime` service account, `/healthz` startup probe.
