- `cloudflare-edge.tf` — zone data source present; the **Pro-plan WAF entitlement erratum** is documented in the file header (custom WAF `log` action requires Enterprise; Pro is restricted to `block`/`challenge`/`js_challenge`/`managed_challenge`/`skip`). Reviewer must NOT flag the absence of a 24h count-mode window — see "Accepted V3 Deviations" in `architecture_rules.j2`. Cloudflare's auto-applied "Free Managed Ruleset" is the v1 baseline.
- `cloudflare-pages.tf` — Pages project has only non-secret env vars; SSE pass-through verified by Cloudflare default behaviour (no `CachingDisabled` workaround).
