**Evidence source:** Authoritative — `run_pytest_infra` against the named test nodes in Section 5. Supplementary: `search_codebase` on the `.tf` files for the literal acceptance values.
**Severity:** WARNING for missing acceptance criteria; INFO for the documented Cloudflare entitlement deviation; CRITICAL only when a secret would land in a public env block (overlaps `FD3.SEC1` / `FE-AP-18`, which already auto-reject — FD10 itself adds no new auto-rejects).

